Men’s team captain Rogers Kwemoi said they have overcome the initial heartbreak and are raring to go. 

“We will continue exercising unless we are told that the event has been cancelled. Everyone is in good condition and we will not give up,” said Kwemoi who trains at Global Sport Communication camp in Kaptagat. 

Kwemoi, Kandie and Sheila Chelagat were allowed to attend the AK Track and Field Meeting at Nyayo National Stadium this weekend. Each member State will decide when and how to enter the trade pact known as the Economic Partnership Agreements (EPAs). From the two extremes, the BBI is full of promises and perils. Multibillion-shilling programme is aimed at boosting access to sanitation facilities in the city within five years.